{
  "id": "RAW_2bcf1382",
  "title": "什么？！你跟我说 LLM 的最后几层都没啥用？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==&mid=2650450307&idx=1&sn=920be9bea40f8620b84d804923cff60b",
  "date": "2025-11-17 10:42:00",
  "author": "AINLP",
  "siteName": "AINLP",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-right-style:solid;padding:1em;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;border-left-color:rgb(250, 81, 81);font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;border-top-style:solid;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border-radius:6px;outline:0px;margin-top:0px;border-width:0px 0px 0px 4px;border-bottom-style:solid;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1em;border-style:solid;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10px;font-style: italic;\">作者：一脑袋浆糊</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10px;font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1969422373771018562\" target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1969422373771018562</a></span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:PingFang SC, -apple-system-font, system-ui, Helvetica Neue, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 0;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"AINLP\" data-alias=\"nlpjob\" data-from=\"1\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/nW2ZPfuYqSKAnqcViaIWJ40GKChb8uoLoichr44nhO2OSPBzMxhdosvv3Ljc695woogSyoIMlsiaIRuk8ur4jpHZg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"一个有趣有AI的自然语言处理公众号：关注AI、NLP、大模型LLM、机器学习、推荐系统、计算广告等相关技术。公众号可直接对话双语聊天机器人，尝试对对联、作诗机、藏头诗生成器、自动写作等，查询相似词，测试NLP相关工具包。\" data-id=\"MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px 0px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">最近刷到三篇相似方向的文章，很难不拿来一起比较，三篇文章看着跟连续剧似的，分别是：</span></p>\n    <pre style=\"border-radius:8px;padding:0 !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.5;\"><code data-language-pending=\"\" data-raw-code=\"1. HOW DO LLMS USE THEIR DEPTH? 后称怎么用文\nhttps://arxiv.org/abs/2510.18871\n\n2. What Affects the Effective Depth of Large Language Models? 后称效率文\nhttps://openreview.net/pdf?id=ILuhAig8xo\n\n\n3. DR.LLM: DYNAMIC LAYER ROUTING IN LLMS ，后称动态文\nhttps://arxiv.org/abs/2510.12773\" data-show-line-number=\"false\" style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:0.5em 1em 1em;margin:0;text-indent:0;white-space:nowrap;display:-webkit-box;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">1. HOW DO LLMS USE THEIR DEPTH? 后称怎么用文</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.18871\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.18871</a></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">2. What Affects the Effective Depth of Large Language Models? 后称效率文</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://openreview.net/pdf?id=ILuhAig8xo\" target=\"_blank\">https://openreview.net/pdf?id=ILuhAig8xo</a></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">3. DR.LLM: DYNAMIC LAYER ROUTING IN LLMS ，后称动态文</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.12773\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.12773</a></span></code></pre>\n    <h1 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"padding:0 1em;margin:2em auto 1em;font-weight:bold;display:table;border-bottom:2px solid #FA5151;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">『一句话』总结三篇文章</span></h1>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">开玩笑，一句话总结不了，因为观点有冲突。 三篇文章都在概念上把LLM切成了三段，接近输入层的</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">输入段</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">，接近输出的</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">输出段</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">，远离输入输出的</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">中间段</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">效率文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">用Transformer每两层之间的层hidden 算cosine similarity，如果cosine similarity远大于0，则说明hidden的方向不再显著调整，作者认定这种【不再显著调整方向】属于低效，并认为大部分LLM不管大小都存在相似程度的</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">低效</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">怎么用文 认为LLM在输入段先基于经验猜一个结果，经过</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">中间段</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">的调整后，到</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">输出段</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">还要</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">反复纠结许久</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">；一个显著的现象是，Topk token的排序在LLM</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">输出段</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">仍然在‘</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">大幅重排</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">’。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">动态文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;给每层做了个“</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">跳过</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">”，“</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">重播</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">”和“</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">正常播放</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">” 的三选一按键，先用蒙特卡洛树搜索（MCTS）采了一些能让LLM效果变好的路径，再给每个层配一个MLP去学习这个开关，得到了In-Domain上</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">略好</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">一点的推理结果。</span></p>\n    <h1 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"padding:0 1em;margin:2em auto 1em;font-weight:bold;display:table;border-bottom:2px solid #FA5151;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">关键细节</span></h1>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0;border-left:3px solid #FA5151;font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;line-height:1.2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">1. 效率文的观察结果对，但观察结论过于武断</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">效率文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">中跟踪观察了，Transformer每个层之间cosine similarity 的变化，并以此作为层使用效率的评价依据。比如下图中，作者把多种模型的每层Attention Output之间，MLP Output之间的cosine similar算出来，形成的这个图。</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100021249\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.4351851851851852\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 4px;aspect-ratio: calc(2.29787) / 1;width: 661px !important;height: auto;\" title=\"null\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=40d7087c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FHrMQ8SF1ApchdqLbWGrbEKQrk2MCyYRPJGfcKcaw28e9V3VZwQu5SPz1CUoLtiapSpDw0woYADSay1Wicug0xfAA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">上图确实展示了：不同模型的共同趋势都是【最后几层的相似度非常高】，并且</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">不拘模型大小，也不拘是否Instruct模型</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">，</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">其实相似的观察，很多前作也有，效率文的创新性其实比较薄。就比如Your Transformer is Secretly Linear 这篇里也有一个类似的图，他把不同种类、不同大小的模型的</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">线性分</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">打了出来（这篇工作用</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">层的hidden去线性拟合</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">层的hidden，拟合优度就是线性分）</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100021250\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.3435185185185185\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 4px;aspect-ratio: calc(2.91105) / 1;width: 661px !important;height: auto;\" title=\"null\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f4f7ec1e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FHrMQ8SF1ApchdqLbWGrbEKQrk2MCyYRPSnGJOuvxRlhmPzgaFd9xicKstwD7Yc38zPdTlH9dwlUvbjOJ91uibE4A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%23imgIndex%3D2\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">上图的左半部分，展示了每层实际hidden（也就是Attention后加回到residual上之后的正常Output）拟合下一层hidden的拟合优度，右半部分跟效率文的视角就比较接近，用Attention Output去拟合下一层的Attention Output，呈现的趋势和本篇是一致的——输出段的层中，Attention Output之间的线性程度也很高，也就是角度高度相似。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">不过，作者的分析结论却不一定合理，或者说这篇工作的作者其实主动回避了深入讨论层“</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">高效</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">”和层“</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">有用</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">”之间的差异。</span></p>\n    <ol style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-left:1em;margin-bottom:0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"margin:0.2em 8px;display:block;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">1.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">平均视角去观察LLM层的有效性意义不大</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：一些decoding 的文章也会做early exit的工作，但是发现不同难度的任务，甚至具体到不同功能的token上，early exit出现的位置是不相同的，一般会认为需要推理步骤越多的token其使用层数是更多的。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"margin:0.2em 8px;display:block;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">2.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">先确定有什么用，再确定这个用处上是否有效</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">：这里第二个视角错误，就是抛开了某一层特有的功能而用一种“大一统”的视角去讨论Effective。一如视觉模型在讨论输入段提取纹理，中间段整理语义特征，输出段组合判断一样，一些研究LLM模型合并的工作会发现，LLM的不同层负责的功能略有差别，中间段有些特定层对代码任务更敏感，少了就会效果变差，有些层则对数学问题更敏感。本文的立场，就好像让举重运动员和长跑运动员，都适配同一个体能测试标准一样愚蠢（我没有在阴阳什么曾经的领导……）</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">退一步讲，就算用相似度观察，观察层间的平均相似度之后，不看看这些平均之下，谁变了，谁没变吗？</span></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0;border-left:3px solid #FA5151;font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;line-height:1.2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">2.</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">怎么用</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">文从TopK排序角度观察，发现即便接近输出的几层LLM的预测仍在显著变化</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">怎么用</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">文给LLM的每层训练了一个映射回词表的W矩阵，用以观测【直接从这一层输出的话，模型会输出什么样的Token分布】。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">从整体分布变化上，作者得到了几个观测，其一、输入段时</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">LLM更偏好高频概念</span></strong></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100021247\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.4351851851851852\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 4px;aspect-ratio: calc(2.29787) / 1;width: 661px !important;height: auto;\" title=\"null\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2503f8cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FHrMQ8SF1ApchdqLbWGrbEKQrk2MCyYRPLEx2qVojicRo24ia2dNWhG0QIUdwbTOgobmtT6JHRC159of37rWNGmgg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%23imgIndex%3D3\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">其二、输入段的输出分布大概率（80%以上）会背推翻（下图算的就是每一层的输出被后面层改掉的比例）</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100021246\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.32685185185185184\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 4px;aspect-ratio: calc(3.05949) / 1;width: 661px !important;height: auto;\" title=\"null\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=74c580eb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FHrMQ8SF1ApchdqLbWGrbEKQrk2MCyYRPFpoR2pHrib09OCgccBAm6DZTPHZx4sOlzdMicDrNmNJYjscTRsZNIFMA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%23imgIndex%3D4\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">其三、即便到了输出段，输出token的分布仍然在显著变化。 下面这张图比较绕，画得是样本有n%样本的正确答案在Rank-1(下图实线）/有n%的样本，正确答案没进Top-k，这种变化的情况确实也是有些LLM early exit不一定能拿到好结果的部分原因。</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100021248\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.2850779510022272\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"898\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 4px;aspect-ratio: calc(0.778163) / 1;width: 661px !important;height: auto;\" title=\"null\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6e1421f3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FHrMQ8SF1ApchdqLbWGrbEKQrk2MCyYRPY7YjxAWhqL2a1PJRJvD3ibJ0TLibUvFN76fHUmeeNTPRAIWBkicocRkTA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%23imgIndex%3D5\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0;border-left:3px solid #FA5151;font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;line-height:1.2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">3. 动态文 给每层装了个跳过/重播键——但……</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">↑这个【但】放到本节最后。 其实就LoopTransformer这个方向看（不一定是latent space reasoning方向，Loop Transformer基本上都是不同形式可循环的Transformer结构的研究），目前效果比较好的是Block-Wise的Loop，也有Token Wise的By Layer决定是否单层Loop的工作（Inner Thinking Transformer），但之前的工作大多数没有把跳过和重跑放到一个框架里考虑。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;动态文给每层都安了一个</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">三选一</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">的决策按钮——一个MLP层，去决定本层是 【跳过】（跑0次），还是【重播】（其实是指</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">跑两遍</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">），还是【继续】（正常跑）。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">在这个功能的加持下，LLM【并没有】获得更好的结果（In-Domain有涨1%左右，但Out-of-Domain跌1%左右 ，下面+Router就是作者的方法）</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100021251\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.3685185185185185\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 4px;aspect-ratio: calc(2.71357) / 1;width: 661px !important;height: auto;\" title=\"null\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0c3e42ad&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FHrMQ8SF1ApchdqLbWGrbEKQrk2MCyYRPmYRnnFHdBrFftCANCnkERZEwRRkfwtib0sPk8rhaicoEE6bDDul3Xe2Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%23imgIndex%3D6\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">作者的训练方案是：用蒙特卡洛树搜索采样了相对效果最好的&lt;层路径&gt;（每层也只有跳过/重播/继续 这三种选择，针对</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">层的LLM训练了&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">个路由器，每层一个。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">只不过，在&lt;预料之外，情理之中&gt;的是</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">其实MCTS实际采样出来的绝大部分路径还是顺着正常前向走</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">，具体看下图。 下图中作者把多个数据集中用MCTS采样后得到的行动决策数展示了出来，图上几乎难以见到【重播】，在ARC数据集上还能见到一点比例的【跳过】。</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100021252\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.6277777777777778\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 4px;aspect-ratio: calc(1.59292) / 1;width: 661px !important;height: auto;\" title=\"null\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d4f6b775&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FHrMQ8SF1ApchdqLbWGrbEKQrk2MCyYRPibse3ibLryfbScNRXcMlq5BGtzLyohyoM5J2CI0WcrKpYY2XGMqpCbFQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%23imgIndex%3D7\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 0.8em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">在保障了拟合精度的前提下，这样训练出的控制键</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">反而是对原本的前向没有太大改变的</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">。 本节标题里有个【但……】，指的就是，作者的训练方案没有作用在基于Loop训练的Transformer上，可能</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">从根本上制约了这种方法的实际能力</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">我在初看这篇文章的时候，第一个疑问就是，他是重训的模型还是在现有的模型上搞的——答，</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">在现有的模型上搞的</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">。我其实非常怀疑这种剥离开预训练的方案到底能不能获得比较显著的提升，从这篇工作的角度看，层数的有效拓展</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">单凭固定层数的预训练显然是不行的</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">（虽然好像某个Loop Transformer的前作也展示了这个观点）。</span></p>\n    <h1 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"padding:0 1em;margin:2em auto 1em;font-weight:bold;display:table;border-bottom:2px solid #FA5151;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">评价</span></h1>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">研究Transformer的层的效率和功能其实是个比较经典的话题，这个话题在今年 Test-time Scaling这个思路打开后，好像在现有的LLM上找到一条更好的推理路径，或者延伸Transformer的实际运算深度就成了一个很热的话题。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">从另一个角度看，我们也可以认为，离散的COT的一部分职能就是给Transformer增加了一个外接的支具或者Checkpoint，以延伸器实际推理深度。而移除外接支具，重新让这种共深度延伸回到自然的模型前向中，是研究latent space reasoning的主要动力之一。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">但是，到现在为止，在共识上其实没有比较好的统一——即，并没有很好的定义用latent space的具体目的——比如，应该获得什么更好的性质？应该补全现有离散空间在处理信息上的什么问题？等等，导致现在latent space reasoning的很多工作，在局部看是很有趣的，但在整个方向的发展脉络上……可能并没有推着整个方向前进。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">当然，研究Transformer层的性质这个方向，本身也是为了带来对Transformer性质的认知，以期能够找到合适的发展方向。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">1.很遗憾的是，效率文这篇工作尽管在很多模型和数据上做了对Transformer的测度，但是这个测度本身其实缺乏新意，也很难说这篇文章真正带来了比较好的认知。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">2.</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">怎么用文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;从一个相对更细致的角度去观察层的功能变化，带来的认知——【LLM是先猜个大概再仔细琢磨，高难问题还会反复纠结】，也有其他工作可以佐证（可以点我头像，找\"LLM怎么做加法\"，或者直接看看Anthropic的文章 On the Biology of LLM )</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">3.</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(250, 81, 81);font-weight: bold;font-size: inherit;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">动态文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">从每层可Loop的角度出发，给每层配了一个用MCTS采样决策的好路径来学习——这个思路其实挺有意思的，就是无法适配到原生Loop Transformer上，同时也无法改变现有Transformer已经训练好，可能已经比较固化的现实。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-align:justify;undefined:text-justify：inter-word;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">写这篇文章的时候，看到Seed的Ouro了，只不过这篇的Abstract就给我看翻白眼 了（我甚至怀疑这个Abstract就是他们这个Loop模型写的，不然怎么跟蛇似的，不能直着说话），但是细看Ouro确实有一些点跟现有的Loop Transformer不同，下一篇写它。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深度对比分析了三篇关于 LLM 层功能与效率的最新研究，揭示了 LLM 内部处理机制的复杂性及当前研究的挑战。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深度对比分析了三篇关于 LLM 层功能与效率的最新研究，揭示了 LLM 内部处理机制的复杂性及当前研究的挑战。",
  "summary": "本文对三篇探讨大型语言模型（LLM）层级工作原理和效率的最新研究进行了详细的对比分析。首先，文章概括了这三篇论文的核心观点：一篇认为 LLM 后期层存在\"低效\"，另一篇则指出 LLM 在输出层仍进行\"大幅重排\"，而第三篇尝试通过动态层路由机制优化。作者随后深入剖析了每篇论文的关键细节，批判性地指出\"效率文\"的观察结论过于武断，\"怎么用文\"通过 TopK 排序观察揭示了 LLM 从\"猜大致结果\"到\"反复纠结\"的推理过程，而\"动态文\"虽有创新思路但受限于训练方案未能显著提升效果。文章最后总结了当前对 Transformer 层效率和功能研究的困境，强调了统一研究目的的重要性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "LLM 的层功能复杂且存在争议，并非简单线性处理。",
      "explanation": "通过对比三篇论文，文章指出 LLM 的各层并非都以相同方式\"高效\"工作，输出层仍在进行关键的 Token 分布调整，推翻了某些关于\"后期层无用\"的武断结论。"
    },
    {
      "point": "LLM 推理过程是\"先猜后纠结\"的迭代优化。",
      "explanation": "“怎么用文”的观察表明，LLM 在输入层倾向于高频概念，随后通过中间层调整，直到输出层仍在显著变化 TopK Token 排序，体现了复杂的决策迭代过程。"
    },
    {
      "point": "现有动态层路由方法在预训练模型上效果受限。",
      "explanation": "“动态文”尝试为 LLM 层引入跳过/重播机制，但由于其训练方案未融入原生 Loop Transformer 的预训练，导致在现有模型上难以获得显著性能提升。"
    }
  ],
